     * @param size     desired size of the slice in bytes; must be &ge; 0; clamped to the available
     *                 bytes if it would extend past the end of the buffer
     * @return a new {@code MemoryRecords} backed by the requested sub-range; never {@code null}
     * @throws IllegalArgumentException if {@code position} or {@code size} is negative, or if
     *                                  {@code position} exceeds the buffer limit
